## ✅ REGRA #9: COMMITS ATÔMICOS

Cada commit deve ter UMA mudança lógica completa:

```
❌ ERRADO
Commit: "Fix bugs and add features"

✅ CORRETO
Commit 1: "feat(products): add tenantId support to products module"
         └─ Schema + DTO + Service + Controller + Tests

Commit 2: "feat(frontend): add tenants dropdown in ProductView"
         └─ Vue component + Pinia store + API calls
```

