## ✅ REGRA #12: SEMPRE USAR PINIA STORE PATTERNS

```vue
❌ ERRADO (state no componente)
<template>
  <div>{{ localCustomers }}</div>
</template>

<script setup>
const localCustomers = ref([]);
onMounted(async () => {
  const response = await fetch('/api/customers');
  localCustomers.value = await response.json();
});
</script>

✅ CORRETO (usar Pinia store)
<template>
  <div>{{ customersStore.customers }}</div>
</template>

<script setup>
import { useCustomersStore } from '@/stores/customers.store';

const customersStore = useCustomersStore();

onMounted(() => {
  customersStore.fetchCustomers(); // handle fetch no store
});
</script>
```

